  "response": "Assessing an individual's mental health, especially that of a public figure like Donald Trump, requires a thorough evaluation by qualified mental health professionals. It's important to rely on credible sources and avoid speculation when it comes to someone's psychological well-being. As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, there has been no official diagnosis or public statement confirming that Donald Trump has a mental illness. If you have concerns about mental health\u2014whether your own or someone else's\u2014it's advisable to consult with a licensed mental health professional.",
